Interface Concern

All Superinterfaces:
org.nasdanika.common.Adaptable, org.nasdanika.ncore.Documented, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.nasdanika.ncore.Marked, org.nasdanika.persistence.Marked, ModelElement, org.nasdanika.ncore.ModelElement, org.nasdanika.ncore.NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
ConcernImpl
public interface Concern extends ModelElement
A representation of the model object 'Concern'. An interest in a system relevant to one or more of its stakeholders.

The following features are supported:

  • Stakeholders
  • Viewpoints
